[{"id": 333, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Call the Pack</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You are not alone in any wilderness.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, creatures of the local environment respond \u2014 describe what arrives and how it affects the <strong>Scene</strong>. The GM honors it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They remain for the rest of the <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 334, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Wildform</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: the animal is closer to the surface.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, your senses are sharpened \u2014 ambush finds no opening against you, and you gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on any <strong>Perception</strong> or <strong>Nature</strong> check.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You also <strong>Sense</strong> hidden creatures nearby.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 335, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Camouflage</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You become part of what's already there.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Stealth</strong> check. On success, you and up to two allies are <strong>Hidden</strong> as long as you remain still \u2014 the environment absorbs you.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Hidden persists even through slow movement.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 336, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bloom</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Things grow when you pay attention to them.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, accelerate growth in the immediate environment \u2014 this creates one new physical feature the GM must acknowledge: cover, difficult terrain, a climbable surface, or food.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Create two features, not one.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 337, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Nature's Veil</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The forest closes around you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally would be hit, perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, terrain or growth interposes \u2014 they gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> equal to the environment's density, as the GM describes.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You also gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 338, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Stone Skin</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The mountain is not indifferent. It is patient.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, your skin hardens \u2014 gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> and any <strong>Strike</strong> you absorb this <strong>Scene</strong> is reduced to its minimum effect.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Extend stone skin to one ally touching you.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 339, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Grove's Gift</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The grove tends to what you bring into it.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Nature</strong> check. On success, choose one ally's spent or failed card from this <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 it is refreshed and returned to their hand with <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> attached.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Refresh a second card from any ally.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 340, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Into the Fray</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't approach. You arrive.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, close any distance and <strong>Strike</strong> before anyone can react.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> An ally gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> against this target.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is <strong>Rattled</strong> \u2014 the charge came from nowhere.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 341, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Spend the Fury</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Everything you've been holding \u2014 all of it, now.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Spend your entire Rage pool. Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, for each die spent, name one thing you break, move, or overwhelm.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One effect leaves a permanent <strong>Scene</strong> change.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 342, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Reckless Strike</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You stop caring about what happens to you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check with <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> with full force \u2014 you are <strong>Exposed</strong> until your next turn.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Add a Rage die to your pool.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 343, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Break</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">There is no obstacle. There is only physics.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, smash a piece of the <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 an object, barrier, or structure is destroyed and the GM narrates one consequence on any enemy adjacent to it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Their armor is compromised \u2014 they are <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 344, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Grin And Bear It</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Add it to the collection.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When you would lose any <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> from a single <strong>Action</strong> or round of <strong>Combat</strong>, narrate the physical scar it gives you. Then replace all lost <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> by rolling new ones.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 345, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Battle Cry</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The sound alone changes the calculus.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Intimidation</strong> check. On success, all enemies in the <strong>Scene</strong> are <strong>Rattled</strong> \u2014 all allies gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Add a Rage die to your pool.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 346, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Retaliate</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Pain is information. Your response is immediate.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When you lose a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>, perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check \u2014 add a Rage die to your pool, then roll it. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> whatever hit you using that die as <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 347, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Frenzy</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: the anger is running the show now.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, every time you lose a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span>, add a Rage die to your pool. Every <strong>Strike</strong> gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>. Your instinct has only one gear \u2014 set aside any <strong>React</strong> cards in hand. They wait until Frenzy clears.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Add two Rage dice instead of one on next hit taken.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 348, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Sundering Blow</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't just hit them. You compromise them.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target, exposing a weakness \u2014 they are <strong>Exposed</strong>. Allies who Strike them this <strong>Scene</strong> gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on that Strike.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> <strong>Exposed</strong> persists into the next <strong>Scene</strong>.</div><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> You gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next Strike against this target.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 349, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Endure</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You have taken worse.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Endurance</strong> check. On success, remove one condition from yourself and add a Rage die to your pool \u2014 the pain becomes fuel.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Remove two conditions. Add two Rage dice.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 350, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shockwave</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The ground disagrees with them.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, slam the ground or a surface \u2014 every enemy nearby is knocked off balance and <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One enemy is also <strong>Rooted</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 351, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Protect the Weak</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Nobody hurts them while you're here.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally would be hit, perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, throw yourself in the path \u2014 take the hit instead and add a Rage die to your pool.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Immediately <strong>Strike</strong> whoever hit you.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 352, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Primal Roar</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not a sound. A statement.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Intimidation</strong> check \u2014 add all Rage dice in your pool to the roll. On success, the <strong>Scene</strong> stops. Every enemy must spend their next <strong>Action</strong> responding to your presence.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One enemy retreats immediately.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 353, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Blood for Blood</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The score isn't settled. Not yet.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Spend Rage dice equal to the <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> you've lost this <strong>Scene</strong>. Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> with force equal to what you've endured \u2014 the GM matches the narrative weight.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is <strong>Exposed</strong> and <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 354, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Read the Field</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You stopped swinging long enough to look.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Tactics</strong> check. On success:</div><div class=\"co\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"ql\"><div class=\"qi\">Where is the greatest threat in this <strong>Scene</strong>?</div><div class=\"qi\">Where is the safest position right now?</div><div class=\"qi\">What does your enemy most want to protect?</div></div><div class=\"etxt\" style=\"margin-top:4px;\">Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next <strong>Action</strong> that responds to the answer.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> An ally also gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 355, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hold the Line</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Nobody gets through.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When something moves through your position or past an ally beside you, perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, it does not reach its destination this beat.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> It is worse off for trying.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 356, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Press the Advantage</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't stop when they're hurt. That's when you start.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Tactics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> a target that is already <strong>Rattled</strong>, <strong>Exposed</strong>, or <strong>Rooted</strong> \u2014 gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on the strike.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Ally may immediately act on the opening.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 357, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Disarm</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">A fighter without a weapon is just a person in a bad situation.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, a target's weapon, shield, or tool is knocked free \u2014 they are <strong>Exposed</strong> until they retrieve or replace it.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The item lands somewhere inconvenient \u2014 GM decides where.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 358, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Weapon Swap</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The right tool for the right moment.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">At any point, swap your equipped weapon for another in your loadout \u2014 <strong>Draw</strong> one card. The new weapon's passive is immediately active.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next <strong>Action</strong> using the new weapon.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 359, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Covering Fire</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You don't need to hit. You need to make them duck.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Tactics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Strike</strong> at one or more enemies \u2014 whether you hit or not, all allies may <strong>Move</strong> or act freely this beat without being intercepted.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Targets are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 360, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Battlemaster</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You see what they're about to do wrong.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally makes a check, perform a <strong>Tactics</strong> check. On success, give them <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> to add after they see their result.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Give a second ally <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> also.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 361, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Feint</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">They committed to the wrong read.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Deception</strong> check. On success, draw a target's defense to the wrong place \u2014 they are <strong>Exposed</strong> and your next <strong>Strike</strong> against them gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> An ally may immediately act on the opening.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 362, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Arsenal</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: you are never without the right tool.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand, you may use any weapon in your loadout as if it were equipped, without swapping. You have <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on checks where your arsenal is an advantage.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> <strong>Draw</strong> a card when you switch which weapon you use.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 363, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Rally the Line</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You remind them what they're here for.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Leadership</strong> check. On success, every ally in the <strong>Scene</strong> removes one negative condition \u2014 you name what you said, they name how it lands.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Each ally also gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 364, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Grapple</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The fight just became yours to control.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, seize a target \u2014 they are <strong>Rooted</strong> and cannot act freely. You control their position until they break the hold.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 365, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Intercept</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You were already moving to that position.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an ally is targeted, perform a <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Move</strong> to intercept \u2014 gain <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span> and take the hit in their place.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span><strong>Strike</strong> the attacker immediately.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 366, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Overrun</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">You go through, not around.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, <strong>Move</strong> through enemies \u2014 every enemy you pass through is knocked aside and <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> One enemy is also <strong>Rooted</strong> where you left them.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 367, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Shield Slam</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The shield isn't just defense. Not in your hands.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Athletics</strong> check. On success, drive your shield into a target \u2014 they are <strong>Rattled</strong> and <strong>Rooted</strong> where they stand.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also knocked back one position.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}]